er 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Abu Bakr was the most beloved of us to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as he was the best of us and our master.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 7407 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":6674,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/09\/30\/uhud-trembles-khulafa\/","url_meta":{"origin":6674,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Uhud trembles for Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was climbing Mount Uhud with Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman when it began to quake because of them. The Prophet said, \u201cBe still, Uhud! It is but a Prophet, a truthful man, and two martyrs upon you!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-sireen-degrades-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6674,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Sahaba: Whoever degrades Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ayyub reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI suspect that a man who denigrates Abu Bakr and Umar does not love the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3685 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/09\/fadl-abu-bakr-umar-ammar\/","url_meta":{"origin":6674,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Virtues of Abu Bakr, Umar, \u2018Ammar, and Ibn Mas\u2019ud","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Alla